13/05/2005
ISLAMABAD, Pakistan -- Greek Public Order Minister George Voulgarakis signed a police co-operation agreement during his visit to Pakistan on Wednesday (11 May).
He and Pakistani Interior Minister Aftab Ahmed Khan Sherpao expressed interest in boosting co-operation in the areas of terrorism, organised crime, drug trafficking and illegal immigration.
(ANA, Kathimerini - 13/05/05;
MPA - 12/05/05)
